commit 1c5c3b0a19bf370e06a2d2a13c92fa76203fbaaa
Author: Moritz Mack <mmack@apache.org>
Date:   Fri Jan 10 09:47:19 2025 +0100

    Strengthen encryption for elasticsearch-keystore tool to AES 256 (#119749) (#119827)
    
    The latest format version (7) of KeyStoreWrapper will be using a 256
    bits key for the AES cipher.
    
    Closes #ES-10419
    
    Co-authored-by: Felix Barnsteiner <felixbarny@users.noreply.github.com>

